---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Section 8 Pitch Deck"
  description="EduMyna - Building India's Open Education Infrastructure. Revenue-focused, mission-driven, sustainable."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-4xl py-20 md:py-28">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-6">Section 8 Company · Revenue-Generating Social Enterprise</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6">
          EduMyna
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-300 font-light italic mb-8">
          Building India's Open Education Infrastructure
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl">
          Helping 200 million young Indians develop agency, skills, and career readiness through scalable, sustainable programs.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex gap-3 text-sm">
          <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-semibold">Section 8 Company</span>
          <span class="border border-white/20 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">Mission-Driven</span>
          <span class="border border-white/20 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">Sustainable Revenue</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>

  <Container>
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 md:py-24 space-y-24">

      <!-- Slide 2: The Problem -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="problem">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 2</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">The Problem: Education That Fails Students</h2>

        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-2">200 million young Indians</p>
          <p class="text-red-800">will enter the workforce in the next decade with degrees but no practical capability.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">The System Is Broken</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mt-1">×</span>
                <span>Attendance policies prioritize compliance over learning</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mt-1">×</span>
                <span>Theoretical content disconnected from careers</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-slate-400 mt-1">×</span>
                <span>No support for initiative and problem-solving</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">What Students Actually Need</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">✓</span>
                <span>Agency (create opportunities, not wait)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">✓</span>
                <span>Practice-heavy learning (ship real work)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-blue-600 mt-1">✓</span>
                <span>Feedback loops that arrive when useful</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-slate-200">
          Students need transformation, not just information. But the infrastructure to deliver this at scale doesn't exist.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Slide 3: Mission -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="mission">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 3</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Our Mission (Section 8 Social Objective)</h2>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-8 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Mission Statement</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-blue-800">
            To build open, scalable education infrastructure that helps millions of young Indians develop the agency, skills, and career readiness needed to succeed in a rapidly changing world.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Section 8 Social Objectives</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">1. Promote Education</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Provide transformative learning experiences focused on agency and practical capability</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">2. Reduce Inequality</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Keep costs low, prioritize access for socially and economically disadvantaged students</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">3. Build Public Infrastructure</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Open-source technology platform (anyone can self-host)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-5">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">4. Enable Educators</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Give teachers and institutions the tools to run transformative programs</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Revenue ≠ Compromise</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300">
            Revenue is how we <strong>sustain</strong> the mission. We're not grant-dependent. We're not hoping for donations. We generate revenue to ensure the infrastructure exists for the long term.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mt-4">
            Sustainable impact requires sustainable revenue.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Slide 4: Solution -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="solution">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 4</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">The Solution: EduMyna Ecosystem</h2>

        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">EduMyna = Platform + Programs + Policy</p>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">1. EduMyna LMS (Open Source)</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1 ml-6 list-disc">
                <li>Fork of Pupilfirst · Universities can self-host</li>
                <li>Cohort management, submissions, progression tracking, feedback</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">2. Program Delivery (via Partners)</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1 ml-6 list-disc">
                <li>Fund: The Second Design & TinkerHub (distribution partner)</li>
                <li>Run: RealWorldReady programs · Scale: University integration</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">3. Student Acquisition & Marketing</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1 ml-6 list-disc">
                <li>Bring learners to programs · Content marketing, partnerships</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">4. New Tech Products</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1 ml-6 list-disc">
                <li>Tools for education at scale · Built as operational needs arise</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">5. Policy & Partnerships</h3>
              <ul class="text-sm text-slate-700 space-y-1 ml-6 list-disc">
                <li>Government collaboration · University integration · Curriculum policy work</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">The Flagship Program: RealWorldReady</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 mb-4">Not lectures. Practice.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-50">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>30+ sessions on agency, systems thinking, career navigation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="mt-0.5">→</span>
              <span>63% rated sessions 10/10, students report clarity on goals, confidence to act</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold mt-4">Proven pedagogy. Now we scale it.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Slide 6: Why Us -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="credibility">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 6</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Why Us? 12 Years of Credibility</h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">This isn't a new idea. It's 12 years of learnings.</p>

        <div class="relative pl-12 space-y-8">
          <div class="absolute left-3 top-2 bottom-2 w-0.5 bg-slate-200"></div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-9 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-white"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400">2009-2012</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Startup Village (Physical Incubator)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">500 startups, 3,139 jobs, ₹45Cr raised · Learned: Physical doesn't scale</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-9 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-white"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400">2015-2017</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">SV.CO (Digital Pivot)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Online platform, structured cohorts · Learned: Students need skills, not startup advice</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-9 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-white"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400">2017-2018</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Developer Education Experiments</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Apple iOS @ Manipal, Freshworks, Facebook VR · Learned: Mission alignment is operational</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-9 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-900 border-2 border-white"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400">2018-2021</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Pupilfirst (Platform Emerges)</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Built LMS, open-sourced, university deployments · Learned: Education = policy + pedagogy + platform</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute -left-9 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 border-2 border-white"></div>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-slate-400">2022-2024</p>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">The Second Design & RealWorldReady</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">1,500+ learners, 63% rated 10/10 · Learned: Agency + practice = transformation</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-900">4</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">State Governments</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-900">3</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">Tech Giants (FB, Apple, Freshworks)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-5 text-center">
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-900">1,500+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">Students Transformed</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-8 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 text-center">We're not theorizing. We've done this.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Slide 7: Business Model -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="business-model">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 7</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Business Model (Revenue-Generating, Sustainable)</h2>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8">Five revenue streams. NOT VC-dependent.</p>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">1. University Partnerships (B2B2C)</h3>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600">₹2.5-7.5Cr/yr</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Universities pay per student for credit-integrated courses</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Target: 10 universities, 500 students/university/year @ ₹5-15k/student</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">2. Corporate-Sponsored Programs (B2B)</h3>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600">₹1-5Cr/yr</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Companies sponsor programs to build talent pipelines</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Target: 5-10 corporate partners @ ₹10-50L/cohort</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">3. Direct Student Programs (B2C)</h3>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600">₹0.2-5Cr/yr</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Students pay directly for RealWorldReady bootcamps</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Target: 1,000-5,000 students/year @ ₹2-10k/student</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">4. Government Contracts (B2G)</h3>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600">₹1-6Cr/yr</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">State governments fund skill development programs</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Target: 2-3 state partnerships @ ₹50L-2Cr/program</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">5. LMS Hosting & Support (SaaS)</h3>
              <span class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-600">₹1-4Cr/yr</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-2">Universities want hosted Pupilfirst (don't want to self-host)</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Target: 20 institutions @ ₹5-20L/year</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-600 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-green-900 mb-2">Projected Revenue (Year 2-3)</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-900">₹5-25 Crores/year</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-green-800 mt-2">Conservative: ₹5-10Cr · Optimistic: ₹15-25Cr</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Slide 11: The Ask -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="ask">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 11</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">The Ask: Funding & Structure</h2>

        <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-xl p-10 text-center mb-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-blue-200 mb-3">Initial Funding Request</p>
          <p class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-2">₹2-5 Crores</p>
          <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">24-month runway to scale to 10,000 students</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Use of Funds (24 months)</h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-24 text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">40%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Program Delivery & Scaling</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Fund Second Design/TinkerHub, hire facilitators · Target: 10,000 students</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-24 text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">25%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Technology Development</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Fork Pupilfirst → EduMyna LMS, open-source improvements, hosting</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-24 text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">20%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Student Acquisition & Marketing</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Content marketing, university partnerships · Target: 10 universities signed</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-24 text-right">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">15%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Operations & Team + Reserve</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Hire operations lead, compliance, admin, buffer</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-green-900 mb-3">Ideal Funders</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-green-800">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Social impact investors</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>Education-focused foundations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>CSR funds</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-green-600 mt-0.5">✓</span>
                <span>HNIs passionate about education</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-red-900 mb-3">NOT Seeking</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-red-800">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-600 mt-0.5">×</span>
                <span>VC funding (Section 8 = no profit distribution)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-600 mt-0.5">×</span>
                <span>Grant/donation dependency</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Slide 12: Roadmap -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="roadmap">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 12</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Roadmap (Next 24 Months)</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-600 bg-blue-50 pl-6 py-4 rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-blue-900 mb-2">Months 1-6: Foundation</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-blue-800 space-y-1">
              <li>→ Secure funding, fork Pupilfirst → EduMyna LMS</li>
              <li>→ Formalize TinkerHub partnership, sign 3 universities</li>
              <li>→ Run pilot RealWorldReady (500 students), hire core team</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-green-600 bg-green-50 pl-6 py-4 rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-green-900 mb-2">Months 7-12: Scale Programs</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-green-800 space-y-1">
              <li>→ Expand to 10 universities, reach 3,000 students</li>
              <li>→ Sign 2 corporate sponsorships, launch marketing campaigns</li>
              <li>→ Publish impact metrics publicly</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-600 bg-purple-50 pl-6 py-4 rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-purple-900 mb-2">Months 13-24: Achieve Sustainability</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-purple-800 space-y-1">
              <li>→ Reach 10,000 students/year · Revenue: ₹5-10Cr (break-even)</li>
              <li>→ 20+ universities using LMS, 5+ corporate partnerships</li>
              <li>→ 1-2 state government contracts, reinvest surplus</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-3">Long-Term Vision (5 Years)</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">50,000+ students/year · 100+ institutions · National policy influence</p>
          <p class="text-slate-300">Model replicated globally (open-source = anyone can fork)</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Slide 15: Call to Action -->
      <section class="scroll-mt-24" id="cta">
        <div class="inline-block bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Slide 15</div>
